  Release notes
  =============
  
  Unlock the full potential of TRAKTOR 3 in this clear and easy-to-understand
  video tutorial, featuring extensive demonstration clips and detailed 
  commentary from world-renowned artists and TRAKTOR specialists. 
  
  The Native Instruments TRAKTOR 3 Tutorial DVD is the complete guide 
  to the world&#039;s leading DJ software, produced by DJs, for DJs.
  
  Start by mastering the decks and mixer, then discover the secrets of using 
  loops and effects to add dynamics to your sets. Get acquainted with 
  Traktor 3&#039;s highly flexible MIDI features, Beat Grids and advanced 
  mixing techniques, before delving into external controllers and 
  the world of playing live.
  
  Contents:
  
  - Intro
  - Exploring The Decks
  - The Mixer
  - Preparing Loops / Looping On The Fly
  - Integrating Effects & Tempo Synching
  - MIDI Implementation & Controllers
  - Working With Beat Grids
  - Advanced Mixing Techniques
  - Performing Live With Traktor
  - Live Footage
